biography: GDSCs are community groups for students interested in Google developer tech. We are integrated as a division under Sunway Tech Club since 2019.

Hello everyone! 👋 GDSC Sunway is now recruiting our core team for 2023-2024! 🎉

We are delighted to invite talented individuals to join us on this journey! Grab this opportunity to learn, lead and make an impact in Sunway and our community! 🙌 

As long as you are a student at Sunway University, you're welcome to apply to be a part of the core team!

Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!

Closing date: 8/10/2022 (Sunday) @ 11.59pm

Duration of Core Team: October 2023 - July 2024

All Events Recap (Events By Oct 2022 - July 2023 Term Core Team Members)

With this video, we would like to inform you that Core Team Members have reached the end of our term. We wish all the best to the future Core Team Members of GDSC Sunway University! Thank you for your love & support!❤️
#GDSCSunway #CoreTeamMembers

📢 Get ready to enhance your Excel skills with the Excel Workshop, a collaboration between Sunway Analytics Society, Sunway Tech Club and Google Developer Student Clubs Sunway University! Join us for two days of immersive learning and unlock the power of Excel for data analysis and visualization 🚀

In this workshop, you'll delve into the world of Excel, from mastering basic navigation and formulas to exploring advanced search formulas and Visual Basic for Applications (VBA) techniques. Led by our experienced speaker Shong Yang, a Sunway Alumni and Excel expert from the Sunway Tech Club, you'll gain invaluable skills for your academic and professional journey 📊 Shong Yang has been using Excel for nearly 6 years in and outside his accountancy work. Shong Yang has previously conducted intermediate and advanced Excel workshops for Sunway University students, upskilling along the way 🔥

🗓️ Date: 6th & 7th July 2023 (Thursday & Friday)
🕒 Time: 6:00 PM - 8:00 PM
📍 Venue: Lecture Theatre 2, Sunway College

📌 Kindly take note that participants are required to have your LAPTOP FULLY CHARGED before joining the workshop.

🔗 Register now for this exciting Excel Workshop using the registration link below! Limited seats available, so act fast!

Registration Link: https://tinyurl.com/ExcelWorkshop-Registration 

Join us as we empower you with Excel proficiency, enabling you to excel in data analysis and beyond. See you at the workshop! 💪

#sunwayuniversity #sunwaycollege #sunwayanalyticssociety #sunwaytechclub #googledeveloperstudentclubs #SAS #STC #GDSC #mypremierdigitaltech #excel #workshop #excelworkshop

📢 Calling all UI enthusiasts and developers! Are you intrigued by the hype surrounding Tailwind CSS but unsure how to get started? 🤔 Look no further! Join us at GDSC Sunway as we venture into the world of Tailwind CSS and discover how this powerful framework can streamline your UI development process like never before. 🎉

💡 Experience engaging discussions, live demonstrations, and interactive exercises led by Mohammed, a talented Front End Developer, who will share his expertise, best practices, and insider tips to help you create visually stunning and responsive interfaces effortlessly. 🙌 From beginners to seasoned professionals, this event is designed to cater to all skill levels, ensuring that everyone can unlock the full potential of Tailwind CSS. 💪

~GDSC Fireside Jam Ep5: Speed Up Your UI Development with Tailwind CSS~
Details📌
📆 Date: 12 July 2023, Wednesday
🕗 Time: 6:30 PM - 8:30 PM (GMT +8)
🏫 Venue: Lecture Theatre 3, Sunway College
💵 Fee: FREE! 🥳

Requirements🚨
1. Bring your own laptop. 💻
2. Have VS Code installed on your laptop. (https://code.visualstudio.com/)

🎯 Don’t miss this opportunity to enhance your skills, network with industry experts, and stay up-to-date with the latest trends in UI development. 🌐 Limited seats available, so register now via the QR code or link in our bio. See you there! 🤩🌟

#GDSCSunway #TailwindCSS #UIdevelopment #SunwayUniversity #SunwayCollege #GDSC #Technology #FrontEndDeveloper

👨‍💻 Brace yourself for an electrifying journey into the realm of cloud computing with GDSC Sunway! 🚀 Join us for an extraordinary Cloud Workshop where you'll unravel the mysteries behind Google Cloud Platform (GCP) and other leading cloud providers. 🔓 Unlock the potential of AI and ML applications, and discover how Google Compute Engine can revolutionise your LLM training. 🤖

~ GDSC Sunway: Cloud Workshop ~

Hello, Sunwayians! New to Development Operations (DevOps)? Always hearing about it and wish to know more? You are just the right person to join us on GDSC Sunway’s 2 Days DevOps Workshop 🔥! Dive straight into the world of DevOps engineering, understand the job scopes and technologies (e.g. AWS) to streamline your software development and deployment process 💾.

Welcoming our distinguished guest speaker, Elise Ching, a passionate full stack engineer / data scientist! Once a student at Monash University, she is now a senior software engineer at Grab. She will be sharing fundamental concepts of DevOps on Day 1 (during virtual session) and went the extra mile to prepare a beginner-friendly hands-on project on Day 2 (during physical session) just for you! 😎 

Sign up now using the QR code in the poster or the registration link in our bio! Do note that there are limited spots for the physical session, so register quickly if you are interested!

📅Date: 1st June 2023, Thursday
🕜[𝐔𝐩𝐝𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐝]Time: 6:30pm - 8:00pm 
🏫Venue: Online (Bevy)
💵Fees: Free 🥳

Details📌 (Day 2: Physical Session)
📅Date: 2nd June 2023, Friday
🕜[𝐔𝐩𝐝𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐝]Time: 6:30pm - 8:00pm
🏫Venue: Sunway College Classroom (NC-2-30)
💵Fees: Free 🥳

✨ Have you ever looked up into the sky and noticed some blinking lights? Well, believe it or not, those might actually be satellites! But what are they doing up there? Who do they benefit? And how did they even get there in the first place? 🛰️

🚀 Join us at GDSC Sunway for an out-of-this-world sharing session with MEASAT, the leading satellite operator in Malaysia! You’ll get an exclusive look into their day-to-day activities and projects, gain valuable insights into the ever-evolving world of aerospace technology, and engage with MEASAT’s very own engineers in a Q&A session. 🌠

~GDSC Sunway x MEASAT: A Space Collaboration~
📆 Date: Wednesday, 10 May 2023
🕗 Time: 4:00 PM - 6:00 PM (GMT +8)
📍 Venue: Lecture Theatre 3, Sunway University
💵 Fee: FREE! 🎉

Don’t miss this incredible opportunity to broaden your horizons and explore new career paths in the space industry! RSVP now through the QR code or the link in our bio! See you there! 🤩

#GDSCSunway #MEASAT #SpaceTech #Aerospace

🌱 Want to learn how to build APIs with Python and interact with Amazon rainforest data? Join us for GDSC Fireside Jam 3, a hands-on workshop where you'll learn the fundamentals of building APIs with Python! 🚀

👨‍🏫 Led by Shahmir, the Lead of GDSC Sunway University, you'll learn the basics of building APIs with Python, including RESTful architecture, HTTP requests & responses, and JSON data format. Plus, you'll get hands-on experience building an API with Python and tackling the deforestation of Amazon rainforest data.🌳

📅 Date: 28 April 2023 (Friday) 
🕗 Time: 8:00 PM - 9:30 PM (GMT +8)
📍 Venue: Bevy (Virtual Platform) 
💰 Fee: FREE!
🚨 Requirement: Basic knowledge of Python programming + complete set up of Python installer & Visual Studio Code. 💻

Don't miss out on this opportunity to learn from an expert and connect with other developers. Register now through the QR code or the link in our bio! 🌟

#GDSCFiresideJam #BuildingAPIswithPython #PythonProgramming #TechSkillsUpgrade 🚀
